{{nihongo|'''''Jikuu Keisatsu Wecker SIGHT'''''|時空警察ヴェッカーサイト|Jikū Keisatsu Vekkā Saito|''Chrono Police Wecker SIGHT''}} is a [[theatrical production]] from [[Kazuya Hatazawa]]'s ''[[Jikuu Keisatsu Wecker]]'' series (serving as a sequel to ''[[Jikuu Keisatsu Wecker Signa]]'' and ''[[Jikuu Keisatsu Hyperion]]''), planned for limited theatrical release on February 25, 26, and 27, 2011.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ameblo.jp/wecker-sight/entry-10606684377.html |title=公式サイト｜時空警察ヴェッカーサイト制作スタッフのブログ |date=August 1, 2010 |accessdate=August 5, 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024013716/http://ameblo.jp/wecker-sight/entry-10606684377.html |archivedate=October 24, 2012 |df= }}</ref> "SIGHT" stands for "Space-time Inspection Group Hyperion Tactics". [[Honoka Ayukawa]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ameblo.jp/ayukawahonoka/entry-10608605401.html|title=必見!!情報解禁!!｜鮎川穂乃果オフィシャルブログ「鮎川穂乃果ほのぼの日記」by Ameba|date=August 3, 2010|accessdate=August 5, 2010}}</ref> [[Showtaro Morikubo]], and [[Sanshiro Wada]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.musical7.com/stage/636.html |title=舞台「時空警察ヴェッカーSIGHT」 {{!}} ミュージカル７ |date=August 4, 2010 |accessdate=August 5, 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101118033843/http://www.musical7.com/stage/636.html |archivedate=November 18, 2010 |df= }}</ref> all return to perform in the production, following their performances in the ''Wecker Signa'' television series and the ''Hyperion'' film. ''Wecker SIGHT'' serves as the tenth anniversary production for the ''Wecker'' series.

