{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2014}} {{Infobox video game |image = Starpoint_Gemini_Warlords_Steam_capsule_main.jpg |title = Starpoint Gemini Warlords |developer = [[Little Green Men Games]] |publisher = [[Iceberg Interactive]] |engine = |released = 23 May 2017 |genre = [[space combat simulator|Space trading and combat simulator]], [[Role-playing video game|role-playing]], [[4X]] |modes = [[Single-player]] |platforms = [[Microsoft Windows]] }}
'''''Starpoint Gemini Warlords''''' is a blend of [[space combat simulator|space trading and combat simulator]], [[role-playing video game|role-playing]] and [[4X]] video game developed by [[Croatia]]n-based [[Little Green Men Games]] and published by [[Iceberg Interactive]]. ''Starpoint Gemini Warlords'' is a spin-off title to the space sim ''[[Starpoint Gemini 2]]'', which was released in 2014.
==Development== [[Little Green Men Games]] developed ''Starpoint Gemini 2'' based on the community feedback and suggestions in the Steam Early Access program. Although most of the popular suggestions made it in the game, some of the ideas could not be implemented in ''Starpoint Gemini 2''. The feature requests not suitable for ''Starpoint Gemini 2'' were kept on a wishlist and became the base of the new spin-off title ''Starpoint Gemini Warlords''. Just like its predecessor, ''Starpoint Gemini Warlords'' will go through Early Access where the developers intend to implement feature suggestions from their community and change the game according to their feedback. The game was scheduled to stay approximately 6 to 12 months in Steam Early Access and was finished and released after 11 months. <ref name="SPGW_PCgamer">{{cite web|last1=Livingston|first1=Christopher|title=How Early Access will shape Starpoint Gemini Warlords|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/how-early-access-will-shape-starpoint-gemini-warlords/|website=PCgamer|publisher=PCgamer|accessdate=11 May 2016}}</ref> <ref name="SPGW_BluesNews">{{cite web|title=Starpoint Gemini Warlords Early Access|url=https://www.bluesnews.com/cgi-bin/board.pl?action=viewthread&boardid=1&threadid=170795|website=Blue's News|publisher=Blue's News|accessdate=11 May 2016}}</ref>
==Features== ''Starpoint Gemini Warlords'' is a [[role playing video game|role-playing]] [[space combat simulator|space sim]] with a [[4X]] layer. Players can captain various space ships ranging from gunships to carriers and give orders to war fleets on the strategy map. The game takes place in the Gemini System and features pre-scripted story missions (Campaign) and a free roam mode (Conquest).<ref name="SPGW_GamesRing">{{cite web|title=Starpoint Gemini Warlords Gameplay & Early Access Details|url=http://www.gamesring.com/news/starpoint-gemini-warlords-gameplay-early-access-details/|website=Games Ring|publisher=Games Ring|accessdate=12 May 2016}}</ref>
==Release== ''Starpoint Gemini Warlords'' was released on May 23 2017 on Steam and GoG in two versions - Standard and Deluxe Edition. Deluxe Edition includes 160 page full color Artbook, Original Game Soundtrack composed by Nikola Nikita Jeremić, selection of wallpapers and Twitch Overlays.
==Reception== {{Video game reviews |MC = (PC) 75/100<ref name="MCPC">http://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/starpoint-gemini-warlords/critic-reviews</ref> }}
